# Bomberbloke

A multiplayer bomberman clone made in C++.

### Prerequisites

For Ubuntu 20.04 you will need the dependencies SDL2 and ENet.

```
sudo apt-get instal libsdl2-dev libenet-dev cmake make build-essential
```

## Client

You can run the client by using the command
```
./bomberbloke
```

## Server

The server by default uses the port 8888. You can run the server executable using the command

```
./bomberbloke_server
```
